quote.nm: Central New Energy Holding Group Ltd.
quote.summary: Central New Energy Holding Group Ltd, formerly Central Holding Group Co Ltd, is an investment holding company mainly engaged in new energy and engineering procurement construction (EPC) business. The Company operates its business through five segments. The New Energy and EPC segment manufacturing and sales photovoltaic products and EPC. The Green Building and Construction Related Business segment engages in pile cap construction and building works, development, sale and holding properties for investment and leasing purposes, property management and construction materials supply. The Health and Wellness segment provides healthcare consulting and sales of healthcare products and healthy food. The Food and Beverage (F&B) Supply Chain segment provides supply chain of agricultural products, food and beverages. The Smart Energy Management Services segment is engaged in the sales and installation of energy-saving lighting, equipment and information technology development services.
